Subject: Surviving As an Independent Musician
Description: It's hard out there on the streets. Are you a musician trying to get noticed? Or a fan wondering how musicians keep up with work/school/life while still having time and energy for creativity? Come snag some advice from some of the hardest working folks in the area.  Speakers include:Barbeque, Snesei, Walk in Circles, DJ Seanni B, StarF, MPFM, 2d6 - Track: Music  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none

Subject: Performance: Derwood Bowen + 2d6
Description:
An up-and-comer from Westerville, OH, Derwood Bowen has been recording comedy songs, including parody songs, for 10 years, and has been a frequent contributor to the Sideshow at thefump.com. 2d6's rhymes are about the geekiest of geek topics: DIY conventions, Boba Fett, Amedeo Avogadro, daikaiju, geek girls, and the like. 
  Speakers include:Derwood Bowen, 2d6 - Track: Music  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Sound System
